{"tid":2513288,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"尹兆堅子繪畫 冀與父五一同行","createTime":"2021-05-02T11:32:01.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-02T11:43:21.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a091477bca08757895394386ad0361889edaa528","tid":2513288,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T11:32:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210502/7S7UYIVZGJDCBI3BORWGHA4BFI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210502%2F7S7UYIVZGJDCBI3BORWGHA4BFI%2F&d=LCDPOb8M8FyYKm9nuxOGtcyzqlNZT0%2FxJNtMGMfIkD0%3D&h=8bba104f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210502%2F7S7UYIVZGJDCBI3BORWGHA4BFI%2F&h=4081d7ec\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210502/7S7UYIVZGJDCBI3BORWGHA4BFI/</a><br />\n<br />\n尹兆堅子繪畫 冀與父五一同行<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/PfPhswkCHK0QDTDeu4i4EBS-OaI=/510x287/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ZHSTZYWAERCMZHCVMD4RC7HTXE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FPfPhswkCHK0QDTDeu4i4EBS-OaI%3D%2F510x287%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FZHSTZYWAERCMZHCVMD4RC7HTXE.jpg&h=c4e96542&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■尹兆堅兒子為父作畫，指父子被「高牆阻擋」，難在今年五一見到父親身影。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】47名民主派人士因為參加初選被控違反國安法下串謀顛覆國家政權罪，至今只有11人獲准保釋。昨五一勞動節，尹兆堅兒子以畫刻畫父親過去於勞動節參與遊行，為勞工爭取福利的身影，尹子稱明白今年五一不會見到父親。正於羅湖懲教所還柙的袁嘉蔚，向一名中五學生回信，勉勵對方「一起為着未知的未來照顧好自己」。<br />\n<br />\n尹兆堅的fb小編昨發文，題為「尹仔仔：期待同爸爸參加五一勞動節」，並上載尹子的畫作，畫中的尹兆堅正與基層勞工並肩參與遊行。由於尹兆堅於過去的勞動節皆會參與遊行，子女只能於電視新聞中見到父親身影，「佢知道嘅係爸爸出去係幫緊人，幫緊社會有需要嘅人，佢更加知道，今年五一唔會再喺電視搵到爸爸嘅身影，因為一堵高牆阻擋喺佢同爸爸之間。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/NRYJ9iSRLvW4hRR8mh8JwxOXOSI=/510x510/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/OK7ZT44XYZF35KE6V5L2O7JEKU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FNRYJ9iSRLvW4hRR8mh8JwxOXOSI%3D%2F510x510%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FOK7ZT44XYZF35KE6V5L2O7JEKU.jpg&h=8a905ec6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n尹兆堅<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n袁嘉蔚勉中五生照顧好自己<br />\n<br />\n正於羅湖懲教所還柙的袁嘉蔚，其fb小編上載她手繪大樹的獄中回信，惋嘆「我們這個世界啊，不是講道理和邏輯的地方」，袁勉勵該名患有情緒病的中五生，「好好愛自己，一起為着未知的未來照顧好自己」，期待相見。<br />\n<br />\n另外，劉頴匡女友黃于喬昨偕「守護孩子」成員陳伯到荔枝角收押所探望男友，「我同匡都好開心見到陳伯精精神神，正如匡喺庭上所講，佢最希望牆外嘅我哋好好照顧自己，健康安好」。黃透露，劉的囚室滿佈昆蟲及曱甴，劉卻不想殺生，因此每天皆以僅有的資源清潔囚室。當早前用光消毒洗手液後，只好轉用洗髮露充當清潔劑，抹完後整間房充斥濃烈薄荷味。劉同時感激庭上旁聽師、送車師的支持，「希望大家好好照顧自己」。<br />\n<br />\n社民連秘書長吳文遠昨深水埗擺街站時，收到一名跟他同是英文名叫Avery的8歲男童，寫給身在獄中的壹傳媒創辦人黎智英的心意卡。吳在fb分享心意卡內容：「黎智英叔叔，多謝你為所有手足、香港的付出，多謝你！THX！香港人唔會忘記你﹗8歲的Avery上。」稱讚小Avery十分醒目。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/zd3cn6BujEKXPnHNxNuOsZ5ww98=/510x688/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/NVGNTFPMYNFO7HEQZYO52V25XM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fzd3cn6BujEKXPnHNxNuOsZ5ww98%3D%2F510x688%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FNVGNTFPMYNFO7HEQZYO52V25XM.jpg&h=d44862ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■袁嘉蔚在獄中回信，手繪大樹勉勵一名中五生「好好愛自己」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/YL0E9ReCti4Sm1QxjqrbL3kE2ZA=/510x510/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/BAYKANKLDJGQBEBQKZBUG5AQTY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FYL0E9ReCti4Sm1QxjqrbL3kE2ZA%3D%2F510x510%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FBAYKANKLDJGQBEBQKZBUG5AQTY.jpg&h=36ed8e69&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n袁嘉蔚<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/FH27niBnWN1riK4n6mMGLxU2yKc=/510x394/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/4DZHBDQCBFGBXNTFX2STN7FOMU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FFH27niBnWN1riK4n6mMGLxU2yKc%3D%2F510x394%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F4DZHBDQCBFGBXNTFX2STN7FOMU.jpg&h=e87497d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■8歲的Avery在街站填寫心意卡感謝黎智英。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/8JuwW-U6iiYJHDcFr0TqObOfVWw=/510x510/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/6ETNNVK6EFBMZMUPAPSSLDPIKY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F8JuwW-U6iiYJHDcFr0TqObOfVWw%3D%2F510x510%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F6ETNNVK6EFBMZMUPAPSSLDPIKY.jpg&h=3cd9b479&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n黎智英"},{"pid":"1020869aeb32060e6699dfde22f02bb58433777d","tid":2513288,"uid":8500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T11:43:00.000Z","msg":"袁嘉蔚d字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22eb8fc2111c50447c4bc8e9d042fa4090f614e3","tid":2513288,"uid":140924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T11:43:21.000Z","msg":"默默地推<br />\n嘉蔚手字好靚"}]}